the location named 0.1:a is our destination. See that the word is highlighed in the previous sentence.

Use the 'Tab' key to highlight the link. Then press 'e' to open the link.

Links can be written two ways. The first example, above, creates a link to a specific file at a specific location.

Links can also be used to link to a location, providing an inventory of associated files.

